I"n<h2 id="learning-objectives">Learning Objectives</h2>

<p>The learning goals for this module are:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Learn how to estimate and model a trend component;</li>
  <li>Learn how to estimate and model a seasonal component;</li>
  <li>Discuss the difference of deterministic and stochastic trend;</li>
  <li>Discuss stationarity tests to detect trend;</li>
  <li>Develop a script in R to identify and model trend and seasonal component.</li>
</ul>

